                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">被动技能</span></p><p>【被动】战斗开始时，初始附属<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">潜行</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/03/47826599/7b7664a897ad4ff44a0fa76b2b5d1507_3406916308573127143.png",
